lead_paragraph: Chris Archer struck out 10 over 6 2/3 innings to end a 10-start winless streak, and the Tampa Bay Rays beat Kevin Gausman and the Baltimore Orioles 2-0 on Monday night.

headline.print_headline: Archer Has 10 Strikeouts, Rays Beat Gausman, Orioles 2-0
